    <h3 id="membership">Parish Membership</h3>
    <p>
        We welcome all newcomers moving into our parish.  Please call the
        parish office to make an appointment to register with Monique Becker (538-4933).
        If you are moving from the parish, please contact the parish office.
    </p>

